title: The Wonder Years Discography (2006-2015) MP3
description:
PLEASE PLEASE PLEASE go out and support these guys if you like what you hear. These are some great guys making some great music. Go buy an album or a t-shirt or see them in concert, they are great!
 
http://thewonderyearsband.com/
 
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Wonder_Years_(band)



Genre: Pop Punk, Emo-pop, Melodic Hardcore
Codec: MP3
Bit Rate: 192 - 320 kbps

(2006) Bangarang - The Wonder Years [EP] [Split]
(2007) Get Stoked on It!
(2007) Tour [EP]
(2008) Won't Be Pathetic Forever
(2009) Distances [EP] [Split]
(2009) I Refuse to Sink - A Collection of Prior Recordings
(2010) The Upsides
(2011) Suburbia I've Given You All and Now I'm Nothing
(2013) The Greatest Generation
(2015) No Closer to Heaven

This is a pretty good and complete discography. Some songs aren't in 320 kbps so if you can get them better let me know I'd love to have them. All the studio releases should be complete except for Suburbia I've Given You All and Now I'm Nothing which isn't the deluxe version. Also not sure if I have all the EPs/Splits but there are still some extra goodies in here!
